Package: xlversion
Title: Versioning and change tracking for Excel files (.xlsx)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Vera", "Gonçalves", , "vera.maria.dg@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: xlversion provides tools to create fingerprints, snapshots, 
    and intelligent comparisons of Excel files at the sheet level. 
    Ideal for version control, auditing, regulatory compliance and data pipelines.
